  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522070/extras/cbd4a9b21d25c6b5d05a2c395e399032.poster.avif?t=1628415270\" width=616 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522070/extras/cbd4a9b21d25c6b5d05a2c395e399032.webm?t=1628415270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522070/extras/cbd4a9b21d25c6b5d05a2c395e399032.mp4?t=1628415270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Zenith Into Maronarium is hybrid arcade game that includes scroll-shooting, 2d platforming and 3d exploration missions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Plot:</h2>As samozbor menace engulfs the Earth you escape on your faithful Kotel One aircraft. Your last mission is to survive. Can you find winged doom and make it to serve you?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game contains:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenging general gameplay<br></li><li>13 stages divided in 3 episodes<br></li><li>Creepy atmosphere of the ancient videogames<br></li><li>Hard bosses<br></li><li>Hidden tutorial that makes no sense<br></li><li>No hope</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522070/extras/cbd4a9b21d25c6b5d05a2c395e399032.poster.avif?t=1628415270\" width=616 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522070/extras/cbd4a9b21d25c6b5d05a2c395e399032.webm?t=1628415270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522070/extras/cbd4a9b21d25c6b5d05a2c395e399032.mp4?t=1628415270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Zenith Into Maronarium is hybrid arcade game that includes scroll-shooting, 2d platforming and 3d exploration missions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Plot:</h2>As samozbor menace engulfs the Earth you escape on your faithful Kotel One aircraft. Your last mission is to survive. Can you find winged doom and make it to serve you?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game contains:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenging general gameplay<br></li><li>13 stages divided in 3 episodes<br></li><li>Creepy atmosphere of the ancient videogames<br></li><li>Hard bosses<br></li><li>Hidden tutorial that makes no sense<br></li><li>No hope</li></ul>",
